data: This is a pilot initiative and breaks new ground.  West Suffolk College will use extensive resources, facilities, organisational reach and expertise to break down barriers among those outside of the education arena – and bring them into our orbit.  Through project-based learning, this initiative expects to create transformational educational platforms which will create their own impetus and lead to new learning lifestyles and in turn – to greater employment opportunities, increased participation in education and training; and a more ‘connected’ business community.
